# Fieldmark Platform Helpers

Use these instead of ad-hoc `ENV.fetch`, raw Anthropic calls, or one-off demo scripts.

**Related rules:** `rails_ai.mdc` (Claude stack), `rails_services.mdc`, `rails_controllers.mdc`, `project_context.mdc`

---

## Quick reference

| Helper | File | Use when |
|--------|------|----------|
| `Ai.ask` / `Ai.chat` | `api/app/services/ai.rb` | Any Claude text response |
| `Ai.json` | `api/app/services/ai.rb` | Claude must return structured JSON |
| `AiRouter` | `api/app/services/ai_router.rb` | **Never** from feature code — only via `Ai` |
| `RescuesAi` | `api/app/controllers/concerns/rescues_ai.rb` | Controller calls Claude (chat or report enqueue) |
| `AppConfig` | `api/lib/app_config.rb` | Reading environment variables |
| `CurrentSeason` | `api/lib/current_season.rb` | Season year for costs, benchmarks, scenarios |
| `DemoSeed` | `api/app/services/demo_seed.rb` | Repeatable Vibeathon / local demo data |
| `ApiTestHelpers` | `api/test/support/api_test_helpers.rb` | Integration tests against JSON API |
| `GenerateAnalystReportJob` | `api/app/jobs/generate_analyst_report_job.rb` | Async lender report generation |
| `PerplexityRouter` | `api/app/services/perplexity_router.rb` | **Never** from feature code except `MarketIntelligenceService` |
| `MarketIntelligenceService` | `api/app/services/market_intelligence_service.rb` | Live cited `regional_risk` (Perplexity retrieval; Claude interprets) |

