## `AppConfig` — environment variables

**Rule:** Never call `ENV.fetch` in controllers, services, or initializers. Add a method to `AppConfig` and a commented line in `api/.env.example`.

```ruby
AppConfig.anthropic_api_key   # nil if missing
AppConfig.anthropic_model     # default: claude-sonnet-4-6 (AiRouter::SONNET_STABLE_MODEL)
AppConfig.perplexity_api_key  # nil if missing — live regional_risk only
AppConfig.perplexity_model    # default: sonar
AppConfig.jwt_secret_key
AppConfig.cors_origins        # array of strings
AppConfig.redis_url
AppConfig.demo_email          # default: demo@fieldmark.app
AppConfig.demo_password       # default: FieldmarkDemo2026! (set DEMO_PASSWORD in .env)
```

Loaded early via `require_relative` in `api/config/application.rb` (before Devise initializer).

