## `DemoSeed` / `CapeGirardeauSampleSeed` — demo + Cape Girardeau test data

```bash
cd api
bin/rails demo:seed           # demo@fieldmark.app only (from cape_girardeau_sample.json)
bin/rails demo:reset
bin/rails sample_data:seed    # 8 farmers, ~33 fields in Cape Girardeau County
bin/rails sample_data:reset   # drops @cape.fieldmark.app users, re-seeds all
```

Edit farmers/fields in `api/db/seeds/cape_girardeau_sample.json`. `db:seed` in development runs full sample unless `SKIP_CAPE_SAMPLE=1`.

| ENV | Default |
|-----|---------|
| `DEMO_EMAIL` | `demo@fieldmark.app` |
| `DEMO_PASSWORD` | `FieldmarkDemo2026!` |

Each farmer: farm (lat/lng in county), multiple fields with boundaries, input costs, Base Case scenario + peer comparison. Benchmarks loaded if missing.

