## Adding a new helper

1. One clear entry point (`self.call` or module method).
2. Document in this file + `.env.example` if config-related.
3. Add a Cursor rule section or cross-link from `rails_ai` / `rails_services`.
4. Add integration test or extend `api_smoke_test.rb` when behavior is user-facing.
